snippet.title: Ether One PlayStation 4 Trailer
snippet.description:
Official Website: http://www.ether-game.com
Company Website: http://www.whitepapergames.com
Twitter: @WhitePaperGames

Ether One is a first person adventure game based on dementia. We received critical and popular acclaim on PC and we're now bringing our game to the Playstation 4! 

Ether One has been nominated for a Develop award for 'Use of Narrative' & was also a Finalist at Indiecade 2014.
